    "textAr": "أَلَمْ تَرَ كَيْفَ فَعَلَ رَبُّكَ بِأَصْحَـٰبِ ٱلْفِيلِ",
    "textEn": "Have you not considered, [O Muḥammad], how your Lord dealt with the companions of the elephant?",
